## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
- `./gradlew assembleDebug` — Build must complete without errors

### Manual Verification
1. Open Settings > Components > Drivers → verify MTR, GN chips plus new "Installed" chip
2. Click "Installed" chip in Drivers → should show all installed drivers
3. Click `+` button while in Drivers tab → tooltip should say "Install Driver"
4. Click `+` button while in DXVK tab → tooltip should say "Install DXVK"  
5. Open Game Settings > Settings > Graphics → verify `+` button is gone from Graphics Driver dropdown
6. Launch an Epic game → verify it starts correctly without X connection crash
